Subject: Huawei HG default WEP/WPA generator

Hi,

Huawei HG520 and HG530 routers are vulnerable to weak cipher attacks.
It  is possible to generate the default WEP/WPA key from the MAC
address.

The following documents detail the process of developing a key
generator for these devices.

English: http://websec.ca/blog/view/mac2wepkey_huawei

Español: http://websec.mx/blog/ver/mac2wepkey_huawei
